## DEST\_ATOP\_I variable

Porter-Duff operator for packed ints. The destination that overlaps the source is composited with the source and replaces the destination.

[porterDuff](./porter-duff.porterduff.md)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
DEST_ATOP_I: (a: number, b: number) => number
```
